    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "About me ",
        "text_level": 1,
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "I am interested in Computer Vision and NLP topics from research and development perspective.   \nI have experience in these fields in the past over 3.5 years both in industry and academia.   \nI also focussed on time series analysis and signal processing. ",
