    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Efficient MRI Segmentation and Dataset Condensation ",
        "text_level": 1,
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "I explored U-Net and its variants (like U-Net and X-Net), and Vision Transformer for Brain tumor segmentation and classification in MRI datasets. Furthermore, in order to reduce the size of MRI dataset to allow more efficient training, I also performed ‘Dataset Condensation’ that optimizes the original MRI dataset through neural networks. ",
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
