    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Privacy Risks in Machine Learning [1,2,3,4,5,6] ",
        "text_level": 1,
        "page_idx": 6
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Private and Secure Machine learning ",
        "text_level": 1,
        "page_idx": 6
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "I was involved in several topics related to how to not allow any adversary extract sensitive information from machine learning models, and how can one use ML models to extract information from hardware side-channels like cache traces. ",
        "page_idx": 6
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
