    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Text-Signals based Cyberbully Classification ",
        "text_level": 1,
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "In this project, I intended to compete with LLMs like BERT and its variants,   \nbased text classifier, to be competed with simpler   \narchitecture with   \ninnovative “text-signals” as text embeddings. Turns out that this innovation   \nleads to better   \nclassification performance on cyberbully-texts, as   \ncompared to pre-trained LLM based models. ",
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/63788501c19cbd03ce57066ce77bd3ac63ad5735ef06c8f324a54102487bf506.jpg",
        "img_caption": [],
        "img_footnote": [],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Proposed modelshave10 to1000 times lesstotal parametercountthan benchmarkmodels ",
        "page_idx": 7
    },
