    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Having Signal-Like Text Embeddings is Competitive to LLMs for Text Classification [1,2] ",
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Radar based Vital Signs Detection ",
        "text_level": 1,
        "page_idx": 8
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "I worked on full-stack radar based vital signs (heart rate and breathing rate) detection project that uses Doppler radar, in conjugation with Fourier and Empirical Mode based processing to robustly estimate the vital signs and displays them to a user’s smartphone app. ",
        "page_idx": 8
    },
