        "page_idx": 8
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "COVID-19 Contact Tracing [1,2,3,4,5] ",
        "text_level": 1,
        "page_idx": 9
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "In this project, I worked both on client (smartphone, flutter) and development side (nodejs, PostgreSQL) to design an app based solution for contact tracing of COVID-19, using smartphone sensors like GPS, bluetooth (beacon protocol) and accelerometer data. I utilize both algorithm and AI tools to build a unified solution, and I published paper on it. ",
        "page_idx": 9
    },
