        "page_idx": 11
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "I utilized smartphone Bluetooth RSSI values (under Eddystone Beacon protocol) as well as   \naccelerometer,   \ngyroscope and speed   \nsensor values in   \nsmartphone to perform activity   \nclassification, as well as distance estimation using machine learning models. ",
